  },
  {
    q: 'How much does golf cost on the Mornington Peninsula?',
    a: 'Rates vary significantly. Expect to pay a premium at The National and Moonah Links. St Andrews Beach, Mornington, Rosebud, and The Dunes are more accessible in price.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is there accommodation near the Peninsula golf courses?',
    a: 'RACV Cape Schanck Resort is on-site. Moonah Links has nearby accommodation. Read the stay-and-play options for the full picture.',
  },
